                    <li><strong>Natural Saturated Fats:</strong> Testosterone is uniquely synthesized directly from cholesterol. Eating a restrictive ultra-low-fat diet will crush your hormone profile. Embrace natural fats from coconut oil, organic butter, and fatty fish. Understand exactly <a href="which-vitamin-is-essential-for-hair-growth.php">which vitamin deficiencies</a> cripple your natural progress.</li>
                </ul>

